### Get all cities
GET https://localhost:5001/api/cities
Accept: application/json

### Get a specific city (Vancouver - ID 0)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/cities/1
Accept: application/json

### Get points of interest for Vancouver
GET https://localhost:5001/api/cities/1/pointsofinterest
Accept: application/json

### Get a specific point of interest
GET https://localhost:5001/api/cities/1/pointofinterest/1
Accept: application/json

### Create a new point of interest
POST https://localhost:5001/api/cities/0/pointsofinterest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Granville Island",
  "description": "Public market and artisan shops on a small island."
}

### Update an existing point of interest
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/cities/0/pointsofinterest/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Science World Updated",
  "description": "Interactive science museum in a geodesic dome."
}

### Delete a point of interest
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/cities/0/pointsofinterest/2